Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个与命运持续战斗着的男人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙一行人 在和阿蒂妮的海战中取得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战斗中 阳子明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮亚信赖着自己 信赖着大Gurren团这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子对妮亚的不信任也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大Gurren团的羁绊变得更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 你在这儿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗? 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想 妮亚怎么给人印象彻底变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪 一点都不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都在忙着工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人什么都不做 这种事我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做点什么 给大家帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但妮亚是公主嘛 只要这样微笑着...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也对呢...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你又从早上开始什么都没吃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃的时候我也吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开动Lagann的只有你一个 有个万一的时候怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃也是工作之一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃也是工作之一?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰到你们了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也找到答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(痛 痛痛痛 痛啊痛啊痛啊!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 西蒙借我一用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 长不大的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13话 大家多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗修他怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因不明 但看起来身体没什么异状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是积劳过度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是小孩子 却要驾驶Gurren不断战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下也难怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也没资格说别人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近是不是有点努力过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是在干我该干的事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能吃到超~豪华的料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么拚命的妮亚也好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是从昨天起就绝食在等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你那也太过火了吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你打算吃多少啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮亚说她也想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 马上好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那点很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从大小来看应该是战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但显示的坐标指向空中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是敌人真的从天上来的话 要怎么回击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,262)\fs18\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\shad0\bord1\b1}飞行要塞航母型GUNMEN 大GUNTEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了展示我的力量的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋王罗杰诺姆 请好好看着吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体突击!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗修的代理哦 Gurren由我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来有什么不满吗? 我也有好好训练哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不攻过来吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了! 来啊来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来决一胜负吗 胜负!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红叶”接近中!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记着!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事可不会再有下次了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurren-Lagann!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是群葬送了齐米鲁夫和阿蒂妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让古阿姆都颜面扫地的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是他们太弱 是我太强了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达雅卡 Gurren-Lagann要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去也只是给他们当靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再把我们扔出去 利胧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空啰啰嗦嗦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成怎样我都不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 看来能把它收为己用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看来能行!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样和飞行战舰也能一战了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能干啊 那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇悠和奇亚露吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 10倍报复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 可要吃不到妮亚做的大餐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大餐! 大餐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就让他们看看大Gurren团的斗志吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击~开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一口气冲上去了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方GANMEN 高速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还能相见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊 光屁股猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉鲁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白吗 我的无念!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人苟活下来的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和你一战而低声下气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加了今天这场战斗的我的心情!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 还不能熟练控制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不会吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉鲁 和敌方GANMEN一起撞入飞行球控制室中!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 算不了什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有小孩和女人在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那在哪儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥他..已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候..就死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡米那他..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说我是 输给了你吗..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 一个人..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子 我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了之后 把戴着受伤的人当作藉口的话 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANMEN欠下的东西 就用GANMEN来还吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的作风!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前飞行球动力下降中! 无法维持高度!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊 维拉鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他们那边在冒烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会啊 我们上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也被打得很惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮全部损坏 动力室也快成破烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管这种事啊 西蒙他们可是在敌人肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不掩护他们的话又该怎么办啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我飞过去把他们全踢飞!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么区区一个人类小孩!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此做个了结吧 维拉鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真的一个人也能战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,262)\fs18\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\shad0\bord1\b1}西托曼多拉专用特化GANMEN SHEZAKKU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动 那边的GANMEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢动的话 这只母猴子就要变成肉饼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西托曼多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算玩到什么时候 维拉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不听什么藉口 给他最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 西蒙 战斗啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙啊 维拉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 这就是你的作风吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利胧 这么做真的没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就行了 让我推吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我 吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大Gurren 最大战速!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能以这种方式和那个人类做了断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗 维拉鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你捡回来的恩情 看来你也忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉鲁!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞踢啊 飞踢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了完了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 只是擦了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是呢 是卜塔保护了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看来那个就是飞行的动力源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 把那个抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的飞行球被夺走了 飞行机能已经无法维持!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法撑住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉鲁 可不会那么简单就饶了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算把他们赶回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 西蒙 知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 喜欢卡米那哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头和内脏没异常呢 静养一段时间就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太结实也让人头痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子 你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 利胧说得太夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个问题 刚才做好的饭菜 大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了嘛 吃也是工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 还会再来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗修?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实..是昨天的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然被妮亚拜托试吃她做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 实在没法想像是这世界的东西的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对看来很高兴的在做菜的妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能明白地跟她说不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就把所有菜都试吃了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个才..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的失败 全是因为这家伙违反命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又无能又喜欢反抗 简直是个没救的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必 将维拉鲁处以极刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋王 如果您命令我死的话 我甘愿受死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前有事想请您告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 维拉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真的是比兽人低劣的生物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类..到底是什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HO..西托曼多拉 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这男人就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽人还真是不完全的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巨人为了维持肉体 如同死一般的沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在此期间进行的细胞的再生是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是硬要醒过来的话 全身的细胞就会坏死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生产出兽人的是螺旋王您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对这种肉体..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那答案 你真的想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉鲁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多厚的墙都有崩溃的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此坚信着向前冲 和同伴们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 天元突破Gurren-Lagann
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位贵安